you have any friends back at the Armed Forces 
Special Weapons Project that could tell you what

33:24.987 --> 33:36.358
impact it had on them? Well, yes, we worked with 
them constantly, and the impact on them would have

33:37.739 --> 33:47.008
been the same as it was on us, as a matter of fact.

33:48.997 --> 34:02.272
It

33:48.997 --> 34:02.272
had the effect of slowing down our development 
program and making it much more costly.

